description:
Shell scripts for the RNA-Seq analysis of the following study: 

 Fr&ouml;hlich KS, F&ouml;rstner KU, Gitai Z. Post-transcriptional gene regulation by an 
Hfq-independent small RNA in Caulobacter crescentus. Nucleic Acids Res. 2018 Aug 
27.  https://doi.org/10.1093/nar/gky765.  

 The sequencing data are deposited at NCBI GEO under the accession number  GSE104186.  

